{
  "stem": "2966.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we started-- immediately they formed a Jewish [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] committee of a few prominent Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they started asking for-- everybody had to register to go to work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the people on the committee had to assign people-- certain people going here, going there to work.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I myself, was assigned to building streets, roads.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1941, I was 16 years old.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I was assigned to build roads.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we used to take big rocks-- they used to give us big rocks, with a small hammer, and I used to break it up to small pieces.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was our work, day in and day out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some people were taken to build bridges.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and they were treated terribly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were beaten.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Hasidic Jews, they used to pull them by the beards.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They used to cut their beards off.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They used to drown them and have fun, laugh-- the German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was not even the SS at that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was just the Wehrmacht, the German army.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they carried on just as badly as the SS.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] At that time, they still let us live in our home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And-- and November-- that was the first action in July, and I think the second one was in November of 1941.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They asked for all the women, sick people, old people, and children to report to a certain place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Well, whoever reported and they were taken away on-- on trucks to the forest and shot.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I knew quite a few people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and then the winter set in, and we had a very severe winter.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
